Package edu.cmu.cs.prt

package edu.cmu.cs.prt
Contains classes that provide information about the Pittsburgh Regional Transit system.

PrtRealTime provides real-time information.

PrtInfo provides information about stops and routes.

PrtSchedule provides transit scheduling information.

PrtHistoryTable provides historic information about stops and routes.
